text: Sara Andersen (born 15 May 1996 in Farsø) is a Danish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Denmark women's national team. ==Career== Andersen has been capped for the Denmark national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Danish women's footballers Category:Denmark women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Fortuna Hjørring players
